import React from 'react'
import "./input.css"

const Input =()=> {
  return (<>
  <label>First Name
  <input className='fn'/>
  </label>

  <label>Last Name
  <input className='ln'/>
  </label>

  <label>Email
  <input className='email'/>
  </label>

  <label>Phone
  <input className='phone'/>
  </label>
  <label>Password</label>
  <input className='password'/>

  <label>Confirm Password</label>
  <input className='confpass'/>
        
  </>)
}
export default Input;
